                <div class="widget-poll-question">Could you ever design on a tablet?</div>
                
                <form id="poll133" method="post" action="/">
                
                    <div id="show-form133" class="show-form133">
        
        <table><tr><td><input type="radio" id="poll-val-576" name="133" value="576" /></td><td><label for="poll-val-576">Don’t be ridiculous, they’re far too small!</label></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" id="poll-val-577" name="133" value="577" /></td><td><label for="poll-val-577">I can design on anything, and look good doing it!</label></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" id="poll-val-578" name="133" value="578" /></td><td><label for="poll-val-578">If I have to, I’d rather not to be honest.</label></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" id="poll-val-579" name="133" value="579" /></td><td><label for="poll-val-579">I’d like to try it, but I’m sceptical.</label></td></tr><tr><td><input type="radio" id="poll-val-580" name="133" value="580" /></td><td><label for="poll-val-580">If your users use tablets, it makes sense.</label></td></tr></table>        <input type="hidden" value="133" name="poll_id" />
